{"tid":1631422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新文宣 - 股災擠提","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:58.000Z","uid":142314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c375d7d336d2567d303acaf828d74b8dc9a389f","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"政府預計會停市，如果無停，全港市民星期二馬上拋售手上資產，cash is king ，配合擠提畫面，令國際線知道緊急法係終極核爆，世紀惡法，市場對香港作出了重大反應。<br />\n<br />\n配合和理非進場一週，緊急法不會令勇武退場，只會令香港同林鄭一齊攬炒！"},{"pid":"0cf6aa9d69b234e1a01108f63e06bf585bccab0f","tid":1631422,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4eb56423a47d34236a422b711056fa2560349991","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43638148fa639af9adac339f1452d7c0692a4ef6","tid":1631422,"uid":75959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:32:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"97a95d8faee3739e8edd3737084af1b33989114c","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9bd546517b2f55c890eb556033e2bc517a5defb","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c8c5ab3dd56b2b99eb32bafb5e21fd30c81914a","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"791e1da00dc8e68ce28756c7ab3ad5a1a3881844","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e4d224b83abe38212442fb6d51ca69d0374ff19","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:07:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6797442483eadbe0adbe13e2869d64ac1024106","tid":1631422,"uid":142314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:15:58.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}